Package software.leonov.common.util

Miscellaneous utilities.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoCloseables
    A utility class for working with AutoCloseable instances.
    AutoCloser
    An AutoCloseable that collects AutoCloseable resources and closes them all when it is closed.
    Dates Deprecated.
    Java 8+ users should switch to the new Date and Time API.
    Holder<T>
    A mutable reference to any non-null value of type T.
    ImmutablePair<T,​U>
    An immutable Pair of non-null objects.
    JVM
    Utility methods for obtaining information about the state of the Java virtual machine.
    Numbers
    Static utility methods for working with Integers, Longs, Floats, and Doubles.
    Pair<T,​U>
    A container of two possibly null objects.
    Props
    Static utility methods for working with Properties.
    Throwing
    Static utility methods for working with Throwables.
